Package structures.vectors

Class LinkedStack<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • structures.commons.LinkedStructure<T>
      • structures.vectors.LinkedStack<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Generic type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<T>, DataStructure<T>, Stack<T>, Vector<T>

    public final class LinkedStack<T>
extends LinkedStructure<T>
implements Stack<T>, Vector<T>
    Basic implementation of a LinkedStack class using a Linked List. All basic operations are O(1), except for contains() O(n), which we shouldn't be using with a Stack anyways.
